%F A037306 T(n,k) = (Sum_{d|gcd(n,k)} phi(d)*binomial(n/d,k/d))/n, where phi = A000010 = Euler's totient function. Also T(n,k) = A047996(n,k). - _Paul Weisenhorn_, Apr 06 2011
